  "changelog": "# Sharkord Desktop v0.4.3 Beta\n\n## Changes\n\n- Central Direct Messages hub is now available from the Sharkord home/logo entry.\n- Direct Messages now support server-scoped sending, unread/read state, and file upload rules.\n- User profile popovers now include Direct Message, member-since, and manage-user actions.\n- Admin user details now show activity, message/link/file history, storage usage, and quota context.\n- Voice builds now include an Opus codec guard so Desktop/Web audio negotiation stays on `audio/opus`.\n- Stable channel stays unchanged; this build is published to the Beta update channel.\n",
